Class StripeBlueBrick

java.lang.Object
com.example.dmscoursework.View.Brick.Brick
com.example.dmscoursework.View.Brick.BlueBrick.StripeBlueBrick
public class StripeBlueBrick extends Brick
The StripeBlueBrick class inherits from Brick, so it has access to all the same methods as Brick. However, it has its own makeBrick method which allows it to have a unique description. It also is different in that it can generate a crack in its brick when hit as well as repair itself.
